    <title>数据结构1(Data Structure 1)---数组和栈</title>
    <url>/2020/04/29/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B01/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>数据结构算是学习编程的一个基石，希望我的笔记能够带给你更多的知识和帮助！笔记通篇以java语言为主</p>
<h2 id="数组"><a href="#数组" class="headerlink" title="数组"></a>数组</h2><p>数组大家或许都不陌生，要想获得一个数组，首先要定义它</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span>[] arr = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>[<span class="number">3</span>];<span class="comment">//创建数组，里面的数字为数组长度</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> length = arr.length;<span class="comment">//获取数组的长度</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span>[] arr1 = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>[] &#123;<span class="number">90</span>,<span class="number">80</span>,<span class="number">70</span>,<span class="number">60</span>&#125;;<span class="comment">//也可以直接定义数组的同时定义每个数值</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>数组名的下标都是从零开始</strong>，比如下面访问数组中的元素为例：</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> element = arr[<span class="number">0</span>];<span class="comment">//实际操作时大家可以print这个element，结果应该为0</span></span><br><span class="line">arr[<span class="number">0</span>] = <span class="number">99</span>;<span class="comment">//定义值后，print结果为99</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>定义数值后一个个print太过于麻烦，所以我们可以进行<strong>遍历数组</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;length;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="string">"arr element"</span>+i+<span class="string">":"</span>+arr[i]);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//结果为99,98,97</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="数组元素的添加"><a href="#数组元素的添加" class="headerlink" title="数组元素的添加"></a>数组元素的添加</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//解决数组的长度不可变问题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span>[] arr = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>[] &#123;<span class="number">9</span>,<span class="number">8</span>,<span class="number">7</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> dst=<span class="number">6</span>;<span class="comment">//要加入的目标元素</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//创建一个数组是原来数组长度+1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span>[] newArr = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>[arr.length+<span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//原来数组中的数据全部复制到新数组中</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;arr.length;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    newArr[i]=arr[i];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">newArr[arr.length]=dst;<span class="comment">//把目标元素放入新数组最后</span></span><br><span class="line">arr=newArr;<span class="comment">//新数组代替旧数组</span></span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(Arrays.toString(arr));</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//结果为[9,8,7,6]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="数组元素的删除"><a href="#数组元素的删除" class="headerlink" title="数组元素的删除"></a>数组元素的删除</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//如何删除数组中的6</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span>[] arr = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>[] &#123;<span class="number">9</span>,<span class="number">8</span>,<span class="number">7</span>,<span class="number">6</span>,<span class="number">5</span>,<span class="number">4</span>&#125;;<span class="comment">//目标数组</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> dst = <span class="number">3</span>;<span class="comment">//要删除元素下标</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//创建一个数组是原数组长度-1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span>[] newArr = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>[arr.length-<span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//复制原数组中除了要删除的那个元素以外的其他元素</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;arr.length;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(i&lt;dst)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        newArr[i]=arr[i];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;<span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        newArr[i]=arr[i+<span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">arr=newArr;<span class="comment">//新数组代替旧数组</span></span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(Arrays.toString(arr));</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//结果为[9,8,7,5,4]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
